  <p style="margin:0;font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.55;color:#cfd6da;font-family:'Inter Tight',sans-serif,system-ui;">Pick <b>Quick sort</b>, size ~80, press Play. Watch the random pivot partition the bars; the comparison and swap counters tick up live.</p>
